$VISU
Local Integer A_REPONSE
Global Integer GPRE_VIEW
If dim(A_WINDPREV)<=0 : Local Char A_WINDPREV(30) : Endif
Local Mask CONSFAC2 [FAC2]
Gosub HORODAT
Local Inpbox "CONSFAC2" From GFONCTION At A_STAMP With A_WINDPREV Mask [FAC2] As [SIM_]
Grizo [FAC2]5
Boxact [SIM_]
Gosub TITRES
Boxinp [SIM_] Using A_REPONSE
Close Local Inpbox [SIM_]
Close Local Mask [FAC2]
Kill GPRE_VIEW
Return

